posts.post_title: FS: two 1910 T212 Obaks, Coy (150) and Nourse (175)
posts.post_content:
Nourse is sold. Cameron 150 and Sugden 175 added.

All are 1910. 

Don Cameron 150 Subjects PSA 1 – $115
Bert Coy 150 Subjects PSA 1 – $115
Chet Nourse 175 Subjects PSA 3 – sold
Joe Sudgen 175 Subjects PSA 2 – $95


I'll kick in shipping.
